Name: Business Entity Priority Percent CD Consumers
Description: Percentage of commercial district consumers active from FI total over last 180 days. This priority scoring metric measures relative consumer activity for business entity prioritization. Available in both standard and with-neighbors priority scoring contexts.

Name: Business Entity Priority Percent Category Spend
Description: Percentage of category 0 spend from commercial district total over last 180 days. This priority scoring metric measures category spending concentration for business entity prioritization. Available in both standard and with-neighbors priority scoring contexts.

Name: Business Entity Priority Percent Transaction Count
Description: Percentage of business entity transaction count from commercial district category 0 total over last 180 days. This priority scoring metric measures transaction volume concentration for business entity prioritization. Available in both standard and with-neighbors priority scoring contexts.

Name: Business Entity Priority Raw Score
Description: Raw priority score before normalization for business entities. This calculated metric combines multiple factors to create a composite priority score before scaling to 0-1 range. Available in both standard and with-neighbors priority scoring contexts.

Name: Business Entity Priority Normalized Score
Description: Normalized priority score (0-1 scale) for business entities. This final calculated metric scales raw scores to enable consistent prioritization comparison across different FIs and time periods. Available in both standard and with-neighbors priority scoring contexts.

Name: Commercial District Relationship
Description: Relationship type between business entity and commercial district (member or neighbor). This metadata indicates whether the business entity is directly within the commercial district or a neighboring entity included for proximity analysis. Unique to with-neighbors priority scoring context.

Name: Offers Published Count
Description: Number of offers published to consumers for this business entity. This campaign metric measures offer distribution volume and appears in business entity FI summary views for campaign analysis. Unique to business entity FI summary.

Name: Offers Published Unique Consumers
Description: Number of unique consumers who saw offers for this business entity. This campaign metric measures offer reach and appears in business entity FI summary views for campaign effectiveness analysis. Unique to business entity FI summary.

Name: Offers Activated Count
Description: Number of offers activated by consumers for this business entity. This campaign metric measures offer engagement and appears in business entity FI summary views for campaign performance analysis. Unique to business entity FI summary.

Name: Offers Activated Unique Consumers
Description: Number of unique consumers who activated offers for this business entity. This campaign metric measures activation reach and appears in business entity FI summary views for campaign engagement analysis. Unique to business entity FI summary.

Name: Offers Redeemed Count
Description: Number of offers redeemed for this business entity. This campaign metric measures offer completion and appears in business entity FI summary views for campaign conversion analysis. Unique to business entity FI summary.

Name: Offers Redeemed Unique Consumers
Description: Number of unique consumers who redeemed offers for this business entity. This campaign metric measures redemption reach and appears in business entity FI summary views for campaign success analysis. Unique to business entity FI summary.

Name: Entity Status
Description: Status of business entity within Plink system (Not Enrolled/Jump Start/VL Basic/Premium). This metadata categorizes entity engagement level and appears in business entity FI summary for relationship classification. Unique to business entity FI summary.

Name: Entity Featured Status
Description: Whether business entity is connected to a featured store (1 for featured, 0 for not featured). This metadata indicates promotion status and appears in business entity FI summary for marketing prioritization. Unique to business entity FI summary.

Name: Entity Service Area Status
Description: Whether business entity is in the FI service area (part or neighbor of a commercial district). This geographic metadata appears in business entity FI summary for service area analysis. Unique to business entity FI summary.

Name: Consumer Priority Percent CD Spend
Description: Percentage of consumer commercial district spend from consumer total over last 180 days. This consumer priority scoring metric measures district spending concentration for personalized recommendations. Unique to consumer priority scoring.

Name: Consumer Priority Percent BE Spend
Description: Percentage of consumer business entity spend from consumer commercial district total over last 180 days. This consumer priority scoring metric measures entity spending concentration for personalized recommendations. Unique to consumer priority scoring.

Name: Consumer Priority Percent BE from CD FI
Description: Percentage of business entity spend from commercial district FI total over last 180 days. This consumer priority scoring metric measures entity popularity for personalized recommendations. Unique to consumer priority scoring.

Name: Consumer BE Transaction Count
Description: Consumer business entity transaction count over last 180 days. This consumer priority metric measures transaction frequency for personalized recommendation scoring. Unique to consumer priority scoring.

Name: Consumer Priority Raw Score
Description: Raw priority score before normalization for consumer-business entity pairs. This calculated metric combines multiple consumer factors to create a composite priority score before scaling. Unique to consumer priority scoring.

Name: Consumer Priority Normalized Score
Description: Normalized priority score (0-1 scale) for consumer-business entity pairs. This final calculated metric scales raw scores to enable consistent personalized recommendation ranking. Unique to consumer priority scoring.

Name: Consumer Store Score
Description: Consumer affinity score for specific stores. This calculated metric measures consumer preference for individual stores and enables personalized store recommendations. Unique to store scoring.

Name: Consumer Store Source
Description: Source type for consumer-store relationship (featured/engaged/opted-in/top-verified-local/relevant-cd/relevant-cd-neighbor). This metadata indicates how the consumer-store pairing was determined and appears in store scoring for recommendation strategy analysis. Unique to store scoring.

Name: Total Consumers Enrolled
Description: Total number of consumers enrolled in purchase rewards for the FI. This enrollment metric appears in FI summary and measures overall FI customer base size. Unique to FI-level aggregation.

Name: Available Merchants Count
Description: Count of available verified local merchants within FI commercial districts. This merchant metric appears in FI summary and measures merchant network size available to FI customers. Unique to FI-level aggregation.

Name: Offers Activated Available Merchants 30D
Description: Offer activations from available merchants in last 30 days. This campaign metric appears in FI summary and measures recent campaign engagement across the FI's merchant network. Unique to FI-level aggregation.

Name: Offers Redeemed Available Merchants 30D
Description: Offer redemptions from available merchants in last 30 days. This campaign metric appears in FI summary and measures recent campaign conversion across the FI's merchant network. Unique to FI-level aggregation.

Name: Active Merchants Count
Description: Count of active merchants (verified local, not internally registered) within FI commercial districts. This merchant metric appears in FI summary and measures actively participating merchant network size. Unique to FI-level aggregation.

Name: Redemptions Amount 30D
Description: Total redemption savings amount in last 30 days for the FI. This financial metric appears in FI summary and measures customer savings generated through the rewards program. Unique to FI-level aggregation.

Name: Transaction Amount Redemptions 30D
Description: Total transaction amount with redemptions in last 30 days for the FI. This financial metric appears in FI summary and measures spending volume that generated customer savings. Unique to FI-level aggregation.

Name: Active Cardholders 30D
Description: Active cardholders with at least 1 transaction and 1 login in last 30 days. This activity metric appears in FI summary and measures engaged customer base size for the FI. Unique to FI-level aggregation.

Name: Cardholders Covered 30D
Description: Cardholders with transactions in districts with active merchants in last 30 days. This coverage metric appears in FI summary and measures FI customer base with access to rewards. Unique to FI-level aggregation.

Name: Most Common Brand ID
Description: Most frequently associated brand identifier for the raw descriptor. This metadata appears in raw descriptor analysis and indicates the predominant brand linked to the descriptor. Unique to raw descriptor analysis.

Name: Descriptor Status
Description: Processing status of the raw descriptor (skipped/rejected/resolved/pending). This metadata appears in raw descriptor analysis and tracks the descriptor processing workflow state. Unique to raw descriptor analysis.

Name: Commercial District Relationship
Description: Relationship type between business entity and commercial district (member or neighbor). This metadata indicates whether the business entity is directly within the commercial district or a neighboring entity included for comprehensive analysis. Available in business entity + commercial district + FI aggregation.

Name: Consumer Count
Description: Number of unique consumers for the business entity + commercial district + FI combination. This metric measures distinct consumer reach at this specific aggregation level. Available only in business entity + commercial district + FI aggregation.

Name: Offers Published Count
Description: Number of offers published to consumers for this business entity. This campaign metric measures offer distribution volume and tracks marketing reach across the FI customer base. Available only in business entity + FI aggregation.

Name: Offers Published Unique Consumers
Description: Number of unique consumers who saw offers for this business entity. This campaign metric measures offer reach diversity and tracks how many different customers received marketing offers. Available only in business entity + FI aggregation.

Name: Offers Activated Count
Description: Number of offers activated by consumers for this business entity. This campaign metric measures customer engagement with offers and tracks conversion from offer presentation to activation. Available only in business entity + FI aggregation.

Name: Offers Activated Unique Consumers
Description: Number of unique consumers who activated offers for this business entity. This campaign metric measures activation reach diversity and tracks how many different customers engaged with offers. Available only in business entity + FI aggregation.

Name: Offers Redeemed Count
Description: Number of offers redeemed for this business entity. This campaign metric measures final conversion success and tracks completed offer transactions that generated customer savings. Available only in business entity + FI aggregation.

Name: Offers Redeemed Unique Consumers
Description: Number of unique consumers who redeemed offers for this business entity. This campaign metric measures redemption reach diversity and tracks how many different customers completed offer transactions. Available only in business entity + FI aggregation.

Name: Entity Status
Description: Status of business entity within Plink system (Not Enrolled/Jump Start/VL Basic/Premium). This metadata categorizes the merchant relationship level and indicates engagement tier with the platform. Available only in business entity + FI aggregation.

Name: Entity Featured Status
Description: Whether business entity is connected to a featured store (1 for featured, NULL for not featured). This metadata indicates promotional status and marketing priority within the FI's merchant network. Available only in business entity + FI aggregation.

Name: Entity Service Area Status
Description: Whether business entity is in the FI service area (1 for in area, 0 for out of area). This geographic metadata indicates if the merchant operates within the FI's commercial district coverage. Available only in business entity + FI aggregation.

Name: Commercial District Eligibility Status
Description: Whether commercial district is eligible based on having at least 2500 accounts with 1+ transaction and 1+ login in last 30 days (TRUE for eligible, FALSE for not eligible). This qualification metric determines district viability for program participation. Available only in commercial district + FI aggregation.

Name: Commercial District Total Entities
Description: Total number of business entities within the commercial district. This metric measures the complete merchant network size in the district regardless of verification or activity status. Available only in commercial district + FI aggregation.

Name: Commercial District Local Entities
Description: Total number of verified local business entities within the commercial district. This metric measures the qualified local merchant network size available for customer rewards programs. Available only in commercial district + FI aggregation.

Name: Business Entity Transaction Count 30D
Description: Number of business entities in the commercial district that had transactions in the last 30 days. This activity metric measures recent merchant participation and engagement within the district. Available only in commercial district + FI aggregation.

Name: Consumer Count 30D
Description: Number of consumers who transacted in the commercial district in the last 30 days. This activity metric measures recent customer engagement and district utilization. Available only in commercial district + FI aggregation.

Name: Total Consumers Enrolled
Description: Total number of consumers enrolled in purchase rewards program for the FI. This enrollment metric measures the FI's overall customer base size participating in the rewards program. Available only in FI-level aggregation.

Name: Available Merchants Count
Description: Count of available verified local merchants within FI commercial districts. This merchant network metric measures the total merchant inventory available to FI customers for earning rewards. Available only in FI-level aggregation.

Name: Offers Activated Available Merchants 30D
Description: Number of offer activations from available merchants in last 30 days. This campaign performance metric measures recent customer engagement with the available merchant network. Available only in FI-level aggregation.

Name: Offers Redeemed Available Merchants 30D
Description: Number of offer redemptions from available merchants in last 30 days. This campaign conversion metric measures recent customer transaction completion with the available merchant network. Available only in FI-level aggregation.

Name: Active Merchants Count
Description: Count of active merchants (verified local, not internally registered) within FI commercial districts. This merchant activity metric measures the engaged merchant network size currently participating in customer transactions. Available only in FI-level aggregation.

Name: Redemptions Amount 30D
Description: Total dollar amount of customer savings from redemptions in last 30 days for the FI. This financial benefit metric measures the monetary value delivered to customers through the rewards program. Available only in FI-level aggregation.

Name: Transaction Amount Redemptions 30D
Description: Total transaction amount that generated customer redemptions in last 30 days for the FI. This financial activity metric measures spending volume that triggered customer savings. Available only in FI-level aggregation.

Name: Active Cardholders 30D
Description: Number of cardholders with at least 1 transaction and 1 login in last 30 days. This engagement metric measures the active customer base size that is both transacting and digitally engaged with the platform. Available only in FI-level aggregation.

Name: Cardholders Covered 30D
Description: Number of cardholders with transactions in districts with active merchants in last 30 days. This coverage metric measures the FI customer base that has access to earn rewards through available merchant network. Available only in FI-level aggregation.

Name: Unique Account Count (All Time)
Description: Distinct count of bank accounts linked across all time.

Name: Unique OAuth Sessions (All Time)
Description: Total number of OAuth sessions across all time.

Name: Unique OAuth Sessions (Last 7 Days)
Description: OAuth sessions occurring in the last 7 days.

Name: Unique Account Count (Last 7 Days)
Description: Distinct linked accounts observed in the last 7 days.

Name: Offer Activations (L30d)
Description: Offer activations in the last 30 days for a store/business.

Name: Offer Activations (L3060d)
Description: Offer activations from 3060 days ago for a store/business.

Name: Offer Activations (L6090d)
Description: Offer activations from 6090 days ago for a store/business.

Name: Offer Redemptions (All-time)
Description: Offer redemptions for all time for a store/business.

Name: Offer Redemptions (L30d)
Description: Offer redemptions in the last 30 days for a store/business.

Name: Offer Redemptions (L3060d)
Description: Offer redemptions from 3060 days ago for a store/business.

Name: Offer Redemptions (L6090d)
Description: Offer redemptions from 6090 days ago for a store/business.

Name: Offers Published (L30d)
Description: Offers published in the last 30 days for a store/business.

Name: Offers Published (L3060d)
Description: Offers published from 3060 days ago for a store/business.

Name: Offers Published (L6090d)
Description: Offers published from 6090 days ago for a store/business.

Name: Redeemers Unique (L90d)
Description: Unique consumers who redeemed offers in the last 90 days for a store/business.

Name: Activators Unique (L90d)
Description: Unique consumers who activated offers in the last 90 days for a store/business.

Name: Viewers Unique (L90d)
Description: Unique consumers who viewed offers in the last 90 days for a store/business.
